episodes.title: India Oxenberg
episodes.description: India Oxenberg is an Author, Producer and Activist. Oxenberg was born and raised in Los Angeles, California with her actress mother Catherine Oxenberg. After escaping the NXIVM cult, Oxenberg executive produced the critically acclaimed documentary series ‘Seduced: Inside the NXIVM Cult’ for Starz. India also authored a memoir ‘Still Learning’ and narrated the audiobook exclusively available through Audible.
